metadata.name: #include 001
metadata.description:
Each artwork in the #include series (each, a "Word") comprises a library of hand-drawn shapes ("Syllables," excluding my signature). Words will typically comprise x^2 (e.g., 4, 9, 25, 100) Syllables, and the number of Syllables in a given Word will be specified as a Property of the corresponding token. I endeavor for each Syllable in each Word to be unique.

001 is the first Word in the #include series.

Edition of 1. Good luck and godspeed.
